verbose_text: By contrast, the SIRT1 activator, SRT-1720, reduced cell viability compared to ioxitalamate treatment (p < 0.001, as shown by one-way ANOVA, n = 3 experiments), particularly at a high concentration (p = 0.002 and 0.00002 at 2,500 and 5,000 nM, respectively) (XREF_FIG).
evidence: SIRT1 activator, SRT-1720, reduced cell viability
